WEBVTT

00:12:28.597 --> 00:12:32.846
in fact, they disagree
on almost everything.

00:12:32.846 --> 00:12:38.615
But the legitimacy of the campaign
is based on their diverse points of view.

00:12:39.521 --> 00:12:41.762
Over a decade ago,

00:12:41.762 --> 00:12:46.220
I had a comfortable future
working for an investment bank.

00:12:46.220 --> 00:12:50.492
I was as far removed from the world
of civil society diplomacy

00:12:50.492 --> 00:12:52.768
as you can imagine.

00:12:52.768 --> 00:12:54.927
But I took a chance.

00:12:54.927 --> 00:12:56.924
I changed course,

00:12:56.924 --> 00:13:00.284
and on the way, I helped 
to create social movements